HEADWORD: Awesome
<hw>Awe"some</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>Causing
awe; appalling; awful; <as>as, an <ex>awesome</ex> sight</as>.</def>
<rj><au>Wright.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>Expressive of awe or terror.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>An <qex>awesome</qex> glance up at the auld castle.</q>
<rj><qau>Sir W. Scott.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Awesomeness</ent>⟦br⟧
